                <div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:44.45%">
                    <h1 class="header-hero-title">How to Create Notification Services with Redis, Websockets, and Vue.js</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:33.33%">
                    <figure class="wp-block-image size-full show-for-medium"><img loading="eager" src="How%20to%20Create%20Notification%20Services%20with%20Redis,%20Websockets,%20and%20Vue_fichiers/right-side-hero-graphics-1.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-67744"></figure>
