<p>This component uses several attributes:</p>



<ul><li><mark>id=”notification”</mark> is the element id used to reference the element in JavaScript or CSS code<mark>:show=”dismissCountDown”</mark> indicates that the component is visible only when the <mark>dismissCountDown</mark> variable is not null nor 0</li><li><mark>dismissible</mark> adds a small icon in the alert to let the user manually close it</li><li><mark>@dismissed=”dismissCountDown=0″</mark> shows that the alert box will be closed then the value <mark>dismissCountDown</mark> equals 0</li><li><mark>@dismiss-count-down=”countDownChanged”</mark> is the countdown method</li></ul>



<p>Let’s add a few lines of JavaScript to define the variables and methods used by the alert component:</p>



